Detailed Description

Element to put in a MapSafeVector.

Each MapElement describes a loaded map.

Definition at line 29 of file MapStatistics.h.

Member Enumeration Documentation

enum MapElement::status_t
 

Enumeration values:
TOLD_TO_LOAD  The leader has told the module to load the map.
LOADING  The processor is loading the map.
LOADED  The map is fully loaded.
TOLD_TO_DELETE  The leader has told the module to delete the map.
DELETING  The processor is deleting the map.
DELETED  The processor has deleted the map.
